      "amount": "1/4 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "water",
      "amount": "1 1/2 cups"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Combine yam paste, grated ginger, and coconut cream in a bowl.",
    "Add coconut oil and maple syrup; mix until smooth.",
    "Knead rice flour, tapioca starch, and salt in a separate bowl.",
    "Add water and knead for 10 minutes until dough is smooth.",
    "Place dough on a lightly floured surface and roll out to 1/4 inch thickness.",
    "Use a scallop shell as a mold to cut out circles of dough.",
    "Place a spoonful of cherry filling onto the center of each dough circle.",
    "Fold and press the dough to seal the bao.",
    "Steam the baos for 12 minutes.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with a kalamansi slice."
  ],
